parameters.name: $lkp_PMS_Fact_Loss_Keys$
parameters.label: lkp_PMS_Fact_Loss_Keys
parameters.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT PMS_Fact_Loss.Policy_Key as Policy_Key, PMS_Fact_Loss.Claim_Key as Claim_Key, PMS_Fact_Loss.Claim_Number as Claim_Number, PMS_Fact_Loss.Accident_Dt as Accident_Dt FROM PMS_Fact_Loss

order by  PMS_Fact_Loss.Claim_Number,PMS_Fact_Loss.Accident_Dt ,PMS_Fact_Loss.Claim_Key ASC--

parameters.name: $lkp_PMS_Fact_Loss_Keys2$
parameters.label: lkp_PMS_Fact_Loss_Keys2
parameters.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT
 PMS_Fact_Loss.Policy_Key as Policy_Key
, PMS_Fact_Loss.Claim_Key as Claim_Key
, SUBSTRING(PMS_Fact_Loss.Policy_Key,0,LEN(PMS_Fact_Loss.Policy_Key)-3) as Policy_Number
, PMS_Fact_Loss.Accident_Dt as Accident_Dt 
FROM PMS_Fact_Loss

parameters.name: $lkp_view_loss_fact$
parameters.label: lkp_view_loss_fact
parameters.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT View_Loss_Fact.[Part Policy Key] as Part_Policy_Key, 
View_Loss_Fact.[Claim Key] as Claim_Key, 
View_Loss_Fact.[Claim Number] as Claim_Number, 
View_Loss_Fact.[Accident Dt] as Accident_Dt FROM View_Loss_Fact
order by Claim_Number, Accident_Dt --
